      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00101"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb959" type="place">Marienlyst</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41010">Curhaus</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb43570" type="place">Dänemark</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00102"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb734">Bayreuth</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb51375" type="place">Kgl. <anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L01622-1"/>Opern<note type="textConst" corresp="T_L01622-1">Umrahmt, ein Pfeil weist auf »Das
                        andere«.</note>haus</rs>.</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print">Trompeterloge</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00102"/><date when="1906-08-05">5/VIII 06</date></dateline></opener><p>Das <rs type="place" ref="#pmb51377" subtype="implied">andere</rs> ist <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01622-1"/>auch eins<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01622-1">Er spielt auf das <rs type="place" ref="#pmb51377">Festspielhaus</rs> an, in dem die <rs type="person" ref="#pmb13024">Wagner</rs>-Inszenierungen stattfinden.</note>. Ich war gestern <hi n="2" rend="underline">im</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb33031">Parsifal</rs>.</p><closer><signed>Richard</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
